<item>
<title>AI 只有停止回答问题、开始完成任务，才能成为真正的同事</title>
<link>https://the-decoder.com/ai-wont-become-a-real-coworker-until-it-stops-answering-and-starts-finishing-tasks/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://the-decoder.com/?p=37124</guid>
<pubDate>Sun, 28 Jun 2026 12:51:40 +0000</pubDate>
<source>the-decoder.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【the-decoder.com】腾讯与多所中国高校联合发布的一篇综述论文，勾勒了从聊天机器人到“数字同事”的发展路径。研究人员认为，AI 系统只有在持久工作环境中完成完整任务，而不仅仅是生成答案，才能成为可靠的同事。关键在于将持久工作空间与可复用技能相结合。本文《AI won't become a real coworker until it stops answering and starts finishing tasks》首发于 The Decoder。<br/><br/><a href="https://the-decoder.com/ai-wont-become-a-real-coworker-until-it-stops-answering-and-starts-finishing-tasks/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
</item>
